Colombia’s Fabricato Names Cadavid Acting CEO to Replace Zuluaga

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-07-25T21:53:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/colombia-s-fabricato-names-cadavid-acting-ceo-to-replace-zuluaga.html
Fabricato SA,  Colombia ’s biggest
textile maker, named Juan Carlos Cadavid as the acting chief
executive officer starting Aug. 1.  Cadavid will replace Ivan Zuluaga as the company’s head,
according to a regulatory filing. Cadavid holds a master’s
degree in engineering science from the University of Michigan
and is currently the company’s vice-president of marketing, the
filing said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
 bschmidt16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  